    "encrypted": "false",
    "long_instructions": "###Example 1: \"The Enchanted Forest Adventure\"\r\n\r\n**Narrative:** The player is a brave adventurer navigating an enchanted forest to find a hidden treasure. They face magical creatures, make choices about which path to take, and solve riddles to progress.\r\n\r\n**Key Features:**\r\n- Asks three questions \r\n- Uses conditionals for different outcomes based on choices\r\n- Includes user input and simple branching narrative",
    "ai_tutor_available": "false",
    "submittable": "false",
    "hide_share_and_remix": "false",
